#: ../../source/janim/items/effect/clip.rst:2
msgid "clip"
msgstr "clip"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.FrameClip:1 of
msgid "一个用于创建简单矩形裁剪效果的类"
msgstr "A class for creating simple rectangular clipping effects"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.FrameClip:3 janim.items.effect.clip.TransformableFrameClip:3 of
msgid "``clip`` 参数表示裁剪区域的四个边界，分别是左、上、右、下，范围是 0~1 表示百分比"
msgstr ""
"``clip`` parameter represents the four boundaries of the clipping region: left, top, right, bottom, range is 0~1 "
"representing percentages"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.FrameClip:4 janim.items.effect.clip.TransformableFrameClip:7 of
msgid "``debug`` 参数表示是否开启调试模式，开启后裁剪区域外的部分会显示为半透明红色"
msgstr ""
"``debug`` parameter indicates whether to enable debug mode. When enabled, parts outside the clipping region will be "
"displayed as semi-transparent red"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.FrameClip.create_border_rect:1
#: janim.items.effect.clip.TransformableFrameClip.create_border_rect:1 of
msgid "得到裁剪后的显示区域的包围矩形"
msgstr "Get the bounding rectangle of the clipped display region"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.TransformableFrameClip:1 of
msgid "与 :class:`FrameClip` 类似，但支持更多的变换操作（偏移、缩放、旋转）"
msgstr "Similar to :class:`FrameClip`, but supports more transformation operations (offset, scale, rotation)"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.TransformableFrameClip:4 of
msgid "``offset`` 参数表示裁剪区域 x 与 y 方向的的偏移量，单位是百分比"
msgstr "``offset`` parameter represents the offset in x and y directions of the clipping region, unit is percentage"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.TransformableFrameClip:5 of
msgid "``scale`` 参数表示裁剪区域 x 与 y 方向的缩放量，单位是百分比"
msgstr "``scale`` parameter represents the scaling in x and y directions of the clipping region, unit is percentage"

#: janim.items.effect.clip.TransformableFrameClip:6 of
msgid "``rotate`` 参数表示裁剪区域的旋转角度"
msgstr "``rotate`` parameter represents the rotation angle of the clipping region"
